Returning to the UK
When you return, you must follow the rules for entering the UK.
Help and support
If you need urgent consular assistance, contact your nearest British embassy, high commission or consulate. All telephone numbers are available 24/7.
Further information
The Grenada Government Information Service Facebook page has regularly updated information on the Emergency Powers Regulations which include local restrictions.
